<div style='direction:ltr;border-width:100%'>

<div style='direction:ltr;margin-top:0in;margin-left:0in;width:8.0583in'>

<div style='direction:ltr;margin-top:0in;margin-left:0in;width:8.0583in'>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>索引条件下推（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Index
     Condition Pushdown</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）是</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>MySQL</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>5.6</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>版本的新特性，是一种对多列索引的最左匹配原则条件下对索引利用的完善优化。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>索引条件下推把本来由</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Server</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>层做的索引条件检查向下推给存储引擎层处理，以降低回表和访问存储引擎的次数，提高查询效率。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in'><img
src="data:image/png;base64,"
width=299 height=249></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>如果索引中包含</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> WHERE </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>子句中的所有条件，就可以使用索引条件下推来优化查询。它会将</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> WHERE </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>子句中的条件下推到存储引擎层处理，减少数据读取的行数，从而提高查询效率。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>假设有多列索引（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>name, age</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>），需要检索出表中姓名第一个字是张，而且年龄是</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>10</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>岁的所有用户</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;
color:#70AD47'><span style='font-weight:bold'>示例</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#A626A4' lang=en-US>SELECT</span><span lang=zh-CN> </span><span
style='color:#AB5656' lang=zh-CN>* </span><span style='color:#A626A4'
lang=en-US>FROM</span><span lang=zh-CN> user</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";color:#A626A4' lang=en-US>WHERE</span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"' lang=zh-CN> name </span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";color:#A626A4' lang=en-US>LIKE</span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"' lang=zh-CN> </span><span style='font-family:
"Comic Sans MS";color:#50A14F' lang=zh-CN>'</span><span style='font-family:
"Microsoft YaHei UI";color:#50A14F' lang=zh-CN>张</span><span style='font-family:
"Comic Sans MS";color:#50A14F' lang=zh-CN>%' </span><span style='font-family:
"Comic Sans MS";color:#A626A4' lang=en-US>AND</span><span style='font-family:
"Comic Sans MS"' lang=zh-CN> age</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
color:#AB5656' lang=zh-CN>=</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
color:#986801' lang=zh-CN>10</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'
lang=zh-CN>;</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US><span
     style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span></span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>在没有索引条件下推之前，会根据非聚簇索引先找到所有姓名第一个字是张字段所对应的主键</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> id </span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt' lang=en-US>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in'><img
src="data:image/png;base64,"
width=330 height=196></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>然后根据主键</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> id </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>回表查询出所有数据行，再根据返回的数据行的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> age </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>再筛选一次，因此这</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>A</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>个过程需要执行多次回表查询。而且根据最左匹配原则，只能匹配</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> name </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>索引列，没有利用到</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> age </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>的索引列，因索引失效，执行全表扫描</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in'><img
src="data:image/png;base64,"
width=581 height=389></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>开启索引条件下推后，存储引擎会直接在多列索引中对</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> age </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>索引列进行处理，按照</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>age=10</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>过滤，然后再执行回表查询返回数据行，索引生效，执行全索引扫描</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in'><img
src="data:image/png;base64,"
width=582 height=390></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>索引条件下推的思路是充分利用索引列，尽量在查询出整行数据之前过滤无效的数据，减少回表的次数，大提升查询的效率</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-weight:bold'>注</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:2pt;
     margin-bottom:2pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>索引条件下推只能用于</span><span style='font-family:
     "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>range</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>、&nbsp;</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>ref</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>、&nbsp;</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>eq_ref</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>、</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>ref_or_null</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>访问模式。索引条件下推对于联合索引的部分列模糊查找非常有效</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;margin-top:2pt;margin-bottom:2pt;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:2pt;
     margin-bottom:2pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>索引条件下推只能用于</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt'>InnoDB</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>和&nbsp;</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt'>MyISAM</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>存储引擎及其分区表（</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt'>5.6</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>版本不适用分区表查询，</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt'>5.7</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>版本后可以用于分区表查询）</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;margin-top:2pt;margin-bottom:2pt;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;margin-top:2pt;
     margin-bottom:2pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>对</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt'>InnoDB</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>存储引擎，索引条件下推只适用于非聚簇索引。聚簇索引通过一次查询就能取出数据，不需要使用索引下推</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>索引条件下推不支持基于虚拟列上建立的索引，比如函数索引</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>索引条件下推不支持引用子查询的条件</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:13.5pt'><span
style='font-weight:bold'>索引下推的开启和关闭</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>可以通过设置</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>optimizer_switch</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>系统变量，控制索引下推的关闭和开启，默认情况下索引下推开启</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;
color:#70AD47'><span style='font-weight:bold'>示例</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#2E75B5' lang=en-US>SET</span><span lang=zh-CN>
optimizer_switch=</span><span style='color:#70AD47' lang=zh-CN>'index_condition_pushdown=off'</span><span
lang=zh-CN>;</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#2E75B5' lang=en-US>SET</span><span lang=zh-CN>
optimizer_switch=</span><span style='color:#70AD47' lang=zh-CN>'index_condition_pushdown=</span><span
style='color:#70AD47' lang=en-US>on</span><span style='color:#70AD47'
lang=zh-CN>'</span><span lang=zh-CN>;</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>
